1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,879
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala nisu se Marija,Draga braće i sestre u Kristu.

2
00:00:02,879 --> 00:00:10,880
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo svjedočanstvo neizmjerne Bože ljubavi i Božjeg milosrđa

3
00:00:10,880 --> 00:00:16,239
[SPEAKER_00] htjela bi prikazati za mog drago tatu Stjepana,

4
00:00:16,239 --> 00:00:20,879
[SPEAKER_00] koji nas je prije tri mjeseca napustio sa ovo zemaljskog života,

5
00:00:20,879 --> 00:00:24,199
[SPEAKER_00] a u zadnjem telefonskom razgovoru,

6
00:00:24,199 --> 00:00:27,600
[SPEAKER_00] dan prije nego što je otišao sa ovog svijeta,

7
00:00:28,480 --> 00:00:32,719
[SPEAKER_00] bio je jako ponosan i sretan što danas svjedočim Božju ljubav u mom životu.

8
00:00:32,719 --> 00:00:36,719
[SPEAKER_00] A kako ništa nije slučajno,

9
00:00:36,719 --> 00:00:44,799
[SPEAKER_00] tako vjerujem da nije ni slučajno da baš danas svjedočim Božju ljubav u crkvi svetog Stjepana.

10
00:00:44,799 --> 00:00:51,759
[SPEAKER_00] Te bi isto htjela prikazati moju sestru Stefani i moju mamu Edžidiju,

11
00:00:51,759 --> 00:00:54,960
[SPEAKER_00] te za dušu mog pokojnog muža Josipa,

12
00:00:55,600 --> 00:00:58,960
[SPEAKER_00] za sve duše u čistilištu i za obraćenje grešnika.

13
00:01:00,960 --> 00:01:06,540
[SPEAKER_00] Moje ime je Matea, dolazim iz katoličke i sportske obitelji.

14
00:01:07,859 --> 00:01:11,140
[SPEAKER_00] Moj dragi tata se bavio profesionalno nogometom,

15
00:01:11,140 --> 00:01:13,819
[SPEAKER_00] te je igrao za razne poznate klubove,

16
00:01:13,819 --> 00:01:17,180
[SPEAKER_00] kao što su Dinamo, Vartex, Gaku Austriji,

17
00:01:17,180 --> 00:01:19,819
[SPEAKER_00] u Sloveniji, u Ljubljani i Velenju,

18
00:01:19,819 --> 00:01:23,040
[SPEAKER_00] igrao i za prvu španjolsku ligu u Ratzink-Santander.

19
00:01:24,319 --> 00:01:27,680
[SPEAKER_00] Moja draga mama bavila se profesionalno rukometom,

20
00:01:27,680 --> 00:01:33,159
[SPEAKER_00] a moja sestra Stefani bavila se ritmičko-sportskom gimnastikom,

21
00:01:33,159 --> 00:01:35,719
[SPEAKER_00] te je bila više struka državna prvakinja.

22
00:01:35,719 --> 00:01:40,400
[SPEAKER_00] Osnovnu školu sam završila u Poreću,

23
00:01:40,400 --> 00:01:42,959
[SPEAKER_00] a srednju školu sam završila u Međimorju.

24
00:01:45,840 --> 00:01:49,379
[SPEAKER_00] Sa 15 godina su počeli problemi sa mnom,

25
00:01:49,379 --> 00:01:52,299
[SPEAKER_00] tada sam imala viška kilograma

26
00:01:52,299 --> 00:01:55,920
[SPEAKER_00] i djeca u školi su me zadirkivala i zezala.

27
00:01:55,920 --> 00:01:59,680
[SPEAKER_00] Osjećala sam se poniženo i jadno,

28
00:01:59,680 --> 00:02:03,799
[SPEAKER_00] te tu su počeli problemi sa bulimijom i anoreksijom.

29
00:02:03,799 --> 00:02:07,420
[SPEAKER_00] Počela sam pušiti cigarete

30
00:02:07,420 --> 00:02:10,099
[SPEAKER_00] i družiti se sa starijim društvom.

31
00:02:10,099 --> 00:02:13,020
[SPEAKER_00] Moj prvi veći problem,

32
00:02:13,259 --> 00:02:16,300
[SPEAKER_00] koji sam, na žalost, priredila mojim roditeljima,

33
00:02:16,300 --> 00:02:20,419
[SPEAKER_00] je bio kada sam jedan dan iz škole

34
00:02:20,419 --> 00:02:22,219
[SPEAKER_00] došla sa torbom puno marihuane.

35
00:02:22,219 --> 00:02:26,400
[SPEAKER_00] Moji roditelji su tada pozvali policiju,

36
00:02:26,400 --> 00:02:29,759
[SPEAKER_00] te tu počinje mamina potraga za pomoć.

37
00:02:29,759 --> 00:02:37,439
[SPEAKER_00] Odlazim skupa sa mojom mamom prvi put u Međugorje.

38
00:02:37,439 --> 00:02:41,599
[SPEAKER_00] Od moje 15. do 18. godine

39
00:02:41,599 --> 00:02:44,360
[SPEAKER_00] sam prošla razne psihijatrijske ustanove,

40
00:02:44,360 --> 00:02:47,419
[SPEAKER_00] centar za suzbijanje ovisnosti,

41
00:02:47,419 --> 00:02:49,819
[SPEAKER_00] razne zajednice,

42
00:02:49,819 --> 00:02:53,460
[SPEAKER_00] ali nijedna me nije mogla primiti jer sam bila maloljetna.

43
00:02:55,240 --> 00:02:59,020
[SPEAKER_00] Na kraju su me ipak primili u zajednicu Papa Ivan XXIII,

44
00:02:59,020 --> 00:03:03,080
[SPEAKER_00] koja se nalazi u Italiji, iz koje sam i pobjegla,

45
00:03:03,080 --> 00:03:05,259
[SPEAKER_00] nakon tri mjeseca boravka.

46
00:03:05,259 --> 00:03:08,599
[SPEAKER_00] Nakon mog bijega iz zajednice,

47
00:03:08,599 --> 00:03:11,020
[SPEAKER_00] tamo nisam mogla više ostati,

48
00:03:11,020 --> 00:03:13,800
[SPEAKER_00] te su moji roditelji došli po mene

49
00:03:13,800 --> 00:03:16,099
[SPEAKER_00] i vratili smo se u Poreć.

50
00:03:16,099 --> 00:03:21,919
[SPEAKER_00] Nakon toga su odlučili da je pametnije da ne ostanem u Poreću,

51
00:03:21,919 --> 00:03:24,939
[SPEAKER_00] da je bolje da idem kod bake u Međimurje,

52
00:03:24,939 --> 00:03:28,360
[SPEAKER_00] gdje sam živjela četiri godine i završila srednju školu.

53
00:03:29,979 --> 00:03:32,560
[SPEAKER_00] Sa 18 godina odlazim u Zagreb.

54
00:03:32,560 --> 00:03:38,060
[SPEAKER_00] U Zagrebu je sve izgledalo primamljivo,

55
00:03:38,060 --> 00:03:40,879
[SPEAKER_00] svo to blještavilo,

56
00:03:40,879 --> 00:03:43,159
[SPEAKER_00] sav taj lažan sjaj,

57
00:03:43,159 --> 00:03:46,860
[SPEAKER_00] izlazci osobe iz javnog života

58
00:03:46,860 --> 00:03:51,080
[SPEAKER_00] i tako korak po korak

59
00:03:51,080 --> 00:03:54,139
[SPEAKER_00] počela sam se kretati među tim ljudima.

60
00:03:54,139 --> 00:03:57,199
[SPEAKER_00] To su bili pretežno kriminalci,

61
00:03:58,419 --> 00:04:01,599
[SPEAKER_00] poduzetnici, sportaši, manekenke,

62
00:04:01,599 --> 00:04:03,719
[SPEAKER_00] takozvana zagrebačka elita.

63
00:04:03,719 --> 00:04:08,979
[SPEAKER_00] Moj život tada se svodio na izlaske,

64
00:04:08,979 --> 00:04:11,919
[SPEAKER_00] blud, nemoral i drogiranje.

65
00:04:11,919 --> 00:04:16,279
[SPEAKER_00] Moja sestra je sumnjala da se drogiram,

66
00:04:16,279 --> 00:04:18,980
[SPEAKER_00] htjela mi je pomoći,

67
00:04:18,980 --> 00:04:20,920
[SPEAKER_00] ali ja sam to cijelo vrijeme negirala.

68
00:04:20,920 --> 00:04:24,720
[SPEAKER_00] Počela sam sve više izbivati od kuće,

69
00:04:24,720 --> 00:04:27,339
[SPEAKER_00] nisam se htjela suočiti sa njom,

70
00:04:27,339 --> 00:04:30,199
[SPEAKER_00] tj. nisam se htjela suočiti sama sa sobom.

71
00:04:30,199 --> 00:04:34,660
[SPEAKER_00] Na poziv jedne moje prijateljice,

72
00:04:34,660 --> 00:04:37,120
[SPEAKER_00] bivše manekenke,

73
00:04:37,120 --> 00:04:41,300
[SPEAKER_00] završila sam u Beću,

74
00:04:41,300 --> 00:04:43,740
[SPEAKER_00] narođendanu od Saifa Gaddafija,

75
00:04:44,519 --> 00:04:45,839
[SPEAKER_00] sina predsjednika Libije,

76
00:04:45,839 --> 00:04:47,839
[SPEAKER_00] koga su poslije ubili,

77
00:04:47,839 --> 00:04:52,819
[SPEAKER_00] u Libiji i za vrijeme mog druženja sa njim,

78
00:04:52,819 --> 00:04:56,819
[SPEAKER_00] nagledala sam se svega i svačega,

79
00:04:56,819 --> 00:04:59,540
[SPEAKER_00] od prostitucije,

80
00:04:59,540 --> 00:05:03,819
[SPEAKER_00] pa do silovanja i omalovožavanja ženskog roda.

81
00:05:07,040 --> 00:05:13,160
[SPEAKER_00] Vratila sam se u Zagreb i život u Zagrebu mi je bio prilično dosadan,

82
00:05:14,740 --> 00:05:17,560
[SPEAKER_00] s obzirom da sam upoznala najmračniji dio svijeta,

83
00:05:17,560 --> 00:05:19,160
[SPEAKER_00] dok sam bila u Libiji,

84
00:05:19,160 --> 00:05:21,079
[SPEAKER_00] te sam služila zlu,

85
00:05:21,079 --> 00:05:27,360
[SPEAKER_00] i tada mi je bilo puno zanimljivije postati uspješna poslovna žena u kriminalu,

86
00:05:27,360 --> 00:05:32,959
[SPEAKER_00] nego biti manekenka koja je željna pažnja i novaca na račun drugih muškaraca.

87
00:05:35,240 --> 00:05:37,879
[SPEAKER_00] Nakon toga upoznala sam jednog taljana,

88
00:05:37,879 --> 00:05:41,220
[SPEAKER_00] koji je bio jako poznati svjetski prevarant,

89
00:05:41,220 --> 00:05:45,120
[SPEAKER_00] koji me je nakon toga postao partner u kriminalu,

90
00:05:45,120 --> 00:05:50,180
[SPEAKER_00] a s obzirom da sam okusila novac i moć,

91
00:05:50,180 --> 00:05:52,480
[SPEAKER_00] meni se to jako svidjelo,

92
00:05:52,480 --> 00:05:56,079
[SPEAKER_00] te sam počela putovati svijetom sa njim,

93
00:05:56,079 --> 00:06:00,600
[SPEAKER_00] tada me on upoznao sa taljanskom mafijom,

94
00:06:00,600 --> 00:06:04,360
[SPEAKER_00] sa kojom smo krivotvorene novčanice,

95
00:06:04,899 --> 00:06:06,560
[SPEAKER_00] krivomčarili u razne zemlje,

96
00:06:06,560 --> 00:06:11,220
[SPEAKER_00] u Africi smo krivomčarili zlato i djamante za Dubaj,

97
00:06:11,220 --> 00:06:16,040
[SPEAKER_00] u Belgiji i Rimu smo radili milijunske prijevare

98
00:06:16,040 --> 00:06:18,800
[SPEAKER_00] sa obveznicama, sa raznim bankama.

99
00:06:18,800 --> 00:06:26,300
[SPEAKER_00] Sve te radnje koje smo mi radili bile su jako opasne po život,

100
00:06:26,300 --> 00:06:32,220
[SPEAKER_00] te ja kao žena nisam tada imala ničiju ljudsku zaštitu,

101
00:06:32,220 --> 00:06:34,680
[SPEAKER_00] ali zato jesam Božju,

102
00:06:34,680 --> 00:06:42,540
[SPEAKER_00] zbog koje i jesam sada živa, te mogu posvjedočiti veliku Božju ljubav prea meni

103
00:06:42,540 --> 00:06:45,259
[SPEAKER_00] i veliku Božju pobedu nad zlom.

104
00:06:50,920 --> 00:06:53,459
[SPEAKER_00] To je nama tada jako dobro išlo.

105
00:06:53,459 --> 00:06:58,420
[SPEAKER_00] Jednom iz šale, moj partner je, dok smo bili na jednoj večeri,

106
00:06:58,420 --> 00:07:04,620
[SPEAKER_00] iz Rezanci je predstavio mene kao austro-ugarsku princezu.

107
00:07:05,720 --> 00:07:12,939
[SPEAKER_00] ljudi koji su bili prisutni, povjerovali su to, te nam je to još više koristilo u daljnim poslovima i prijevarama.

108
00:07:14,399 --> 00:07:23,220
[SPEAKER_00] To je dosezalo do te mjere da smo išli u Rumunjsku, gdje je on imao prijatelja koji radi lažne dokumente,

109
00:07:24,139 --> 00:07:27,420
[SPEAKER_00] da mi se naprave papiri, da budem i službenog princeza.

110
00:07:27,420 --> 00:07:32,040
[SPEAKER_00] Bogu hvala danas sam Isus, ova princeza.

111
00:07:33,139 --> 00:07:54,379
[SPEAKER_00] To je trajalo jedno vrijeme dok u Italiji, točnije u Rimu, nešto je pošlo po zlu

112
00:07:54,379 --> 00:07:59,819
[SPEAKER_00] i mi smo se morali vratiti u Hrvatsku i odvojiti na neko vrijeme.

113
00:07:59,819 --> 00:08:02,060
[SPEAKER_00] Poslije ga više nikad nisam vidla.

114
00:08:03,819 --> 00:08:12,399
[SPEAKER_00] Nakon povratka u Zagreb, preselila sam se u svoj stan, svjetovno sam tada imala sve,

115
00:08:12,399 --> 00:08:17,800
[SPEAKER_00] živjela sam u luksuznom stanu, vozila sam skupocijeni auto,

116
00:08:17,800 --> 00:08:25,100
[SPEAKER_00] trošila sam 5 do 10.000 eura dnevno, a opet sam bila nezadovoljna.

117
00:08:25,100 --> 00:08:30,899
[SPEAKER_00] Te tu je moj noćni život i konzumacija kokaina došla još više do izražaja.

118
00:08:32,360 --> 00:08:39,620
[SPEAKER_00] Zato sam i konzumirala u nenormalnim količinama kokain koji mi je davao lažan osjećaj savršenosti

119
00:08:39,620 --> 00:08:43,620
[SPEAKER_00] i nedostatak ljubavi koji mi je falio u životu.

120
00:08:45,039 --> 00:08:58,299
[SPEAKER_00] Sjećam se jednog događaja kad smo pod utjecajem kokaina vozili u suprotnom smjeru po zelenom valu i tada sam otvorila prozor u vožnji i pucala u zrak iz pištolja.

121
00:09:01,720 --> 00:09:07,820
[SPEAKER_00] Kako vidite kako utjecaj droge mijenja cijelu svijest i čovjek postaje lud i nenormalan.

122
00:09:09,980 --> 00:09:22,279
[SPEAKER_00] Bogu hvala na moje sestri koje je samo dragi Bog poslao nakon trodnevnog i noćnog drogiranja i predložila mi da li želim ići sa njom u Dubaj.

123
00:09:23,240 --> 00:09:32,620
[SPEAKER_00] I Bogu hvala da sam pristala, da nisam pristala, sigurno bi me našli u stanu predoziranu i mrtvu.

124
00:09:32,620 --> 00:09:41,340
[SPEAKER_00] Sjećam se da sam u Dubini srce i duše htjela se maknuti od svega.

125
00:09:41,340 --> 00:09:48,299
[SPEAKER_00] Umorna sam bila od tog svijeta, ali nisam znala kako.

126
00:09:53,240 --> 00:10:01,220
[SPEAKER_00] Ni u Dubaju nisam bila živjela anđevskim životom, ali sam živjela normalnije u Zagrebu.

127
00:10:01,220 --> 00:10:05,860
[SPEAKER_00] U Dubaju je droga bila zabranjena, samo da ju spomeneš.

128
00:10:05,860 --> 00:10:10,379
[SPEAKER_00] Ali alkohol, blud i nemoral, nažalost nisam zaobišla.

129
00:10:10,379 --> 00:10:13,019
[SPEAKER_00] Te sam tamo ostala dva mjeseca.

130
00:10:13,019 --> 00:10:22,100
[SPEAKER_00] Družila sam se s arapskom elitom, te počela se zabavljati sa jednim jako poznatim italijanskim nogometašem.

131
00:10:23,240 --> 00:10:31,620
[SPEAKER_00] Ali život u Dubaju mi je nakon dva mjeseca postao dosadan, te sam se vratila u Hrvatsku.

132
00:10:31,620 --> 00:10:43,519
[SPEAKER_00] Kada sam se vratila u Hrvatsku, s obzirom da sam cijelo to vrijeme bila dio jedne zločinačke organizacije,

133
00:10:45,299 --> 00:10:50,419
[SPEAKER_00] koja je obuhvaća ne samo u Hrvatsku, nego i šire.

134
00:10:50,419 --> 00:10:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] Uglavnom tijekom mog povratka iz Dubaja u Hrvatsku,

135
00:10:58,220 --> 00:11:00,220
[SPEAKER_00] moj partner je u kriminalu,

136
00:11:00,220 --> 00:11:04,720
[SPEAKER_00] s obzirom da je nestala ogromna svota našeg novca,

137
00:11:04,720 --> 00:11:07,659
[SPEAKER_00] točnije pokrali su nas.

138
00:11:07,659 --> 00:11:12,600
[SPEAKER_00] Oni su mislili da sam ja stajala iza te krađe,

139
00:11:12,600 --> 00:11:15,740
[SPEAKER_00] koji između ostalog bio i dio mog novca.

140
00:11:17,379 --> 00:11:20,500
[SPEAKER_00] Uglavnom oni su htjeli da iz Dubaja dođem u Istanbul.

141
00:11:20,500 --> 00:11:23,720
[SPEAKER_00] Od kad sam otišla iz Dubaja,

142
00:11:23,720 --> 00:11:26,480
[SPEAKER_00] osjećala sam da nešto nije u redu,

143
00:11:26,480 --> 00:11:29,039
[SPEAKER_00] te nisam otišla u Istanbul.

144
00:11:29,039 --> 00:11:35,700
[SPEAKER_00] Nakladno kad sam se vratila u Hrvatsku,

145
00:11:35,700 --> 00:11:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] saznala sam da su me htjeli ubiti.

146
00:11:40,379 --> 00:11:45,139
[SPEAKER_00] Bogu hvala i tada me Bog čuvao,

147
00:11:45,139 --> 00:11:47,980
[SPEAKER_00] pa mogu sada svjedočiti Božu ljubav u mom životu.

148
00:12:00,159 --> 00:12:26,320
[SPEAKER_00] Po povratku u Zagreb,

149
00:12:26,320 --> 00:12:30,019
[SPEAKER_00] upoznajem sada mog pokojnog muža Josipa,

150
00:12:30,159 --> 00:12:33,899
[SPEAKER_00] mi smo se upoznali u jednom izlasku.

151
00:12:33,899 --> 00:12:37,779
[SPEAKER_00] Vratila sam se starom životu

152
00:12:37,779 --> 00:12:41,639
[SPEAKER_00] i naše upoznavanje uopće nije bilo nalik

153
00:12:41,639 --> 00:12:44,360
[SPEAKER_00] normalnom upoznavanju jednog dečka i cure,

154
00:12:44,360 --> 00:12:46,879
[SPEAKER_00] što je šetnjak, hino,

155
00:12:46,879 --> 00:12:49,159
[SPEAKER_00] a kamol je odlazak na svetu misu.

156
00:12:49,159 --> 00:12:52,340
[SPEAKER_00] Mi smo, nažalost,

157
00:12:52,340 --> 00:12:55,820
[SPEAKER_00] radili sve što sam i sama radila prije njega.

158
00:12:55,820 --> 00:12:58,820
[SPEAKER_00] Pili, drogirali se

159
00:12:58,820 --> 00:13:02,360
[SPEAKER_00] i nakon sedam mjeseci našeg takvog druženja

160
00:13:02,360 --> 00:13:03,559
[SPEAKER_00] mi smo se ženili.

161
00:13:03,559 --> 00:13:07,100
[SPEAKER_00] Godinu dana

162
00:13:07,100 --> 00:13:10,899
[SPEAKER_00] nakon našeg zajedničkog bračnog života

163
00:13:10,899 --> 00:13:14,480
[SPEAKER_00] desila se velika tragedija.

164
00:13:14,480 --> 00:13:15,500
[SPEAKER_00] U mom životu

165
00:13:15,500 --> 00:13:20,700
[SPEAKER_00] na mojoj rođendanskoj proslavi

166
00:13:20,700 --> 00:13:23,700
[SPEAKER_00] preminula je moja prijateljica,

167
00:13:23,840 --> 00:13:24,720
[SPEAKER_00] predozirala se.

168
00:13:27,379 --> 00:13:30,019
[SPEAKER_00] S obzirom da se radilo o smrtnu slučaju,

169
00:13:30,019 --> 00:13:35,340
[SPEAKER_00] moj pokojni muž Josip i ja smo bili uhičeni.

170
00:13:35,340 --> 00:13:40,440
[SPEAKER_00] Nedugo nakon toga sam doživjela psihički slom

171
00:13:40,440 --> 00:13:44,820
[SPEAKER_00] te sam završila u psihijatriskoj bolnici na Jankomiru.

172
00:13:44,820 --> 00:13:48,440
[SPEAKER_00] Za to vrijeme je trajao sudski proces.

173
00:13:48,440 --> 00:13:50,259
[SPEAKER_00] Nama se sudilo

174
00:13:50,259 --> 00:13:55,980
[SPEAKER_00] da bi na kraju oba dvoje bili osuđeni na zatvorsku kaznu zatvora.

175
00:13:57,980 --> 00:14:00,740
[SPEAKER_00] I u to vrijeme Josip i ja smo se sudski razvili.

176
00:14:00,740 --> 00:14:05,080
[SPEAKER_00] Dok sam čekala datum odlaska u zatvor,

177
00:14:05,080 --> 00:14:08,120
[SPEAKER_00] odlazim drugi put u Međugorje,

178
00:14:08,120 --> 00:14:10,759
[SPEAKER_00] gdje sam ostala dva mjeseca.

179
00:14:10,759 --> 00:14:16,360
[SPEAKER_00] Iskreno, tada nisam znala di se nalazim.

180
00:14:16,360 --> 00:14:18,740
[SPEAKER_00] Nisam znala što je Međugorje,

181
00:14:18,740 --> 00:14:21,059
[SPEAKER_00] da je to milosno mjesto.

182
00:14:21,059 --> 00:14:25,919
[SPEAKER_00] To je, kako kaže meni jedan drag svećenik,

183
00:14:27,559 --> 00:14:29,080
[SPEAKER_00] Međugorje je nebo na zemlji.

184
00:14:29,080 --> 00:14:34,200
[SPEAKER_00] Ubrzono nakon dolaska u Međugorje

185
00:14:34,200 --> 00:14:36,879
[SPEAKER_00] uslijedile su prve milosti Božje

186
00:14:36,879 --> 00:14:40,039
[SPEAKER_00] po zagovoru naše nebeske majke Marije.

187
00:14:40,039 --> 00:14:45,299
[SPEAKER_00] Naš Bog nas uvijek čeka da mu se vratimo.

188
00:14:45,299 --> 00:14:48,580
[SPEAKER_00] Njemu ne treba dugo kao što je trebalo meni.

189
00:14:48,580 --> 00:14:52,940
[SPEAKER_00] Uslijedile su razne molitve

190
00:14:52,940 --> 00:14:55,659
[SPEAKER_00] od raznih svećenika i egzorcista,

191
00:14:56,539 --> 00:15:00,419
[SPEAKER_00] jer svojim načinom života posljedice grijeha bile su velike.

192
00:15:02,379 --> 00:15:06,019
[SPEAKER_00] U Međugorju tada upoznajem jednog svećenika

193
00:15:06,019 --> 00:15:08,700
[SPEAKER_00] preko kojeg odlazim u Italiju,

194
00:15:08,700 --> 00:15:10,740
[SPEAKER_00] u Čivita Nova di Marque.

195
00:15:10,740 --> 00:15:13,200
[SPEAKER_00] To je jedno mjesto kraja Onkone,

196
00:15:13,200 --> 00:15:17,399
[SPEAKER_00] gdje su molili intenzivno molitve egzorcizma.

197
00:15:18,600 --> 00:15:21,419
[SPEAKER_00] To je bio isto jedan težak period u mom životu,

198
00:15:21,419 --> 00:15:25,799
[SPEAKER_00] ali isto i milosrdan, jer je to bilo Bože čišćenje

199
00:15:25,799 --> 00:15:28,580
[SPEAKER_00] posljed svih grijeha kojim sam uvrijedila moga Boga.

200
00:15:31,059 --> 00:15:32,580
[SPEAKER_00] Dok sam bila u Italiji,

201
00:15:32,580 --> 00:15:35,179
[SPEAKER_00] nazvala me moja mama,

202
00:15:35,179 --> 00:15:37,639
[SPEAKER_00] te mi je rekla da je od strane suda

203
00:15:37,639 --> 00:15:39,120
[SPEAKER_00] došao poziv,

204
00:15:39,120 --> 00:15:42,600
[SPEAKER_00] da se moram javiti na izdržavanje kazne zatvora,

205
00:15:42,600 --> 00:15:45,740
[SPEAKER_00] te sam se morala vratiti u Hrvatsku.

206
00:15:47,740 --> 00:15:51,580
[SPEAKER_00] Te dane, uopće nisam bila svjesna gdje idem,

207
00:15:51,580 --> 00:15:54,659
[SPEAKER_00] uopće nisam znala šta je zatvor,

208
00:15:54,659 --> 00:15:56,919
[SPEAKER_00] niti šta se tamo dešava,

209
00:15:56,919 --> 00:16:00,080
[SPEAKER_00] samo sam čula razne priče

210
00:16:00,080 --> 00:16:02,100
[SPEAKER_00] od ljudi koji su već bili u zatvoru.

211
00:16:02,100 --> 00:16:05,259
[SPEAKER_00] Nakon mjesec dana,

212
00:16:05,259 --> 00:16:08,980
[SPEAKER_00] provedenih u zatvoru u remetincu,

213
00:16:08,980 --> 00:16:12,159
[SPEAKER_00] s obzirom da sam dobila obaveznu mjeru

214
00:16:12,159 --> 00:16:13,799
[SPEAKER_00] lječenja o dovisnosti,

215
00:16:13,799 --> 00:16:17,720
[SPEAKER_00] priselili su me u zatvorsku bolnicu,

216
00:16:17,740 --> 00:16:18,700
[SPEAKER_00] u Zagrebu,

217
00:16:18,700 --> 00:16:21,820
[SPEAKER_00] tamo sam bila sa najvećim kriminalcima,

218
00:16:21,820 --> 00:16:24,220
[SPEAKER_00] sa najvećim kaznama u Hrvatskoj

219
00:16:24,220 --> 00:16:27,840
[SPEAKER_00] i tada kada sam ja bila u zatvoru,

220
00:16:27,840 --> 00:16:29,899
[SPEAKER_00] bila sam svjedok

221
00:16:29,899 --> 00:16:32,460
[SPEAKER_00] da u zatvoru ima droge,

222
00:16:32,460 --> 00:16:33,740
[SPEAKER_00] silovanja,

223
00:16:33,740 --> 00:16:35,220
[SPEAKER_00] maltretiranja,

224
00:16:35,220 --> 00:16:36,240
[SPEAKER_00] tučnjave

225
00:16:36,240 --> 00:16:38,659
[SPEAKER_00] i od strane zatvorenika

226
00:16:38,659 --> 00:16:40,759
[SPEAKER_00] i od strane zatvorskog sustava.

227
00:16:40,759 --> 00:16:45,500
[SPEAKER_00] Htjela bi spomenuti meni

228
00:16:45,500 --> 00:16:46,559
[SPEAKER_00] jako bitnu stvar,

229
00:16:47,740 --> 00:16:50,179
[SPEAKER_00] da za vrijeme mog boravka u zatvoru

230
00:16:50,179 --> 00:16:52,179
[SPEAKER_00] moja sestra

231
00:16:52,179 --> 00:16:54,539
[SPEAKER_00] mi je donjela molitvenik

232
00:16:54,539 --> 00:16:56,940
[SPEAKER_00] 15. četvrtaka Svetoj Riti

233
00:16:56,940 --> 00:17:00,659
[SPEAKER_00] te sam se počela moliti Svetoj Riti

234
00:17:00,659 --> 00:17:04,559
[SPEAKER_00] iz zatvora sam izašla u četvrtak,

235
00:17:05,099 --> 00:17:06,759
[SPEAKER_00] ali ne bilo koji četvrtak,

236
00:17:06,759 --> 00:17:09,160
[SPEAKER_00] nego 15. četvrtak po molitvi

237
00:17:09,160 --> 00:17:10,660
[SPEAKER_00] našoj dragoj Svetici,

238
00:17:10,660 --> 00:17:13,099
[SPEAKER_00] Svetici nemogućeg Svetoj Riti.

239
00:17:15,500 --> 00:17:17,599
[SPEAKER_00] Nakon moge izlaska iz zatvora

240
00:17:17,599 --> 00:17:20,119
[SPEAKER_00] moja sestra

241
00:17:20,119 --> 00:17:22,160
[SPEAKER_00] me upoznala sa svećenikom

242
00:17:22,160 --> 00:17:24,380
[SPEAKER_00] koji je 9 godina

243
00:17:24,380 --> 00:17:25,279
[SPEAKER_00] moj duhovnik,

244
00:17:25,279 --> 00:17:28,220
[SPEAKER_00] a to je Paterilija Grgić,

245
00:17:28,220 --> 00:17:30,720
[SPEAKER_00] upravitelj Hrvatske delegature

246
00:17:30,720 --> 00:17:32,460
[SPEAKER_00] Družbe misjonara

247
00:17:32,460 --> 00:17:33,380
[SPEAKER_00] Krvi Kristove.

248
00:17:35,220 --> 00:17:36,960
[SPEAKER_00] Uz njega sam počela prolaziti

249
00:17:36,960 --> 00:17:38,339
[SPEAKER_00] razne faze života

250
00:17:38,339 --> 00:17:40,160
[SPEAKER_00] i razne molitve.

251
00:17:40,160 --> 00:17:44,119
[SPEAKER_00] Godinu dana sam bila u redu

252
00:17:44,119 --> 00:17:46,579
[SPEAKER_00] i tada sam na poticaj

253
00:17:46,579 --> 00:17:47,480
[SPEAKER_00] mog duhovnika

254
00:17:47,480 --> 00:17:49,880
[SPEAKER_00] zatražila ništa o ženitbe,

255
00:17:49,880 --> 00:17:51,880
[SPEAKER_00] što je na kraju

256
00:17:51,880 --> 00:17:53,700
[SPEAKER_00] i nadbiskupijski duhovni stol

257
00:17:53,700 --> 00:17:55,680
[SPEAKER_00] na kaptolu donio odluku

258
00:17:55,680 --> 00:17:57,059
[SPEAKER_00] da brak nije bio valjan

259
00:17:57,059 --> 00:17:58,519
[SPEAKER_00] iz raznih razloga,

260
00:17:58,519 --> 00:18:00,619
[SPEAKER_00] a najbitnija stavka

261
00:18:00,619 --> 00:18:01,980
[SPEAKER_00] je svetost braka,

262
00:18:01,980 --> 00:18:03,380
[SPEAKER_00] što mi nismo bili

263
00:18:03,380 --> 00:18:04,900
[SPEAKER_00] ni jedan ni drugi svjesni

264
00:18:04,900 --> 00:18:06,619
[SPEAKER_00] kad smo stupili u brak.

265
00:18:06,619 --> 00:18:09,400
[SPEAKER_00] U svemu tome

266
00:18:09,400 --> 00:18:11,779
[SPEAKER_00] sam se opet izgubila,

267
00:18:11,779 --> 00:18:14,019
[SPEAKER_00] počela izlaziti,

268
00:18:14,019 --> 00:18:15,359
[SPEAKER_00] opijati,

269
00:18:15,359 --> 00:18:16,519
[SPEAKER_00] drogirati,

270
00:18:16,519 --> 00:18:18,859
[SPEAKER_00] vratila u staro društvo

271
00:18:18,859 --> 00:18:19,579
[SPEAKER_00] i u kriminal.

272
00:18:19,579 --> 00:18:23,700
[SPEAKER_00] Godinu dana je trajao

273
00:18:23,700 --> 00:18:25,400
[SPEAKER_00] period ludog života,

274
00:18:25,400 --> 00:18:28,180
[SPEAKER_00] nakon čega sam odlučila

275
00:18:28,180 --> 00:18:29,559
[SPEAKER_00] vratiti se u poreć

276
00:18:29,559 --> 00:18:34,079
[SPEAKER_00] i tada mi je Bog čuvao leđa

277
00:18:34,079 --> 00:18:36,380
[SPEAKER_00] nedugo nakon

278
00:18:36,380 --> 00:18:37,839
[SPEAKER_00] moga odlaska iz Zagreba

279
00:18:37,839 --> 00:18:40,039
[SPEAKER_00] cijela organizacija

280
00:18:40,039 --> 00:18:41,059
[SPEAKER_00] je bila uhičena

281
00:18:41,059 --> 00:18:44,339
[SPEAKER_00] skupa sa mojim pokojnim mužem

282
00:18:44,339 --> 00:18:45,039
[SPEAKER_00] Josipom

283
00:18:45,039 --> 00:18:47,720
[SPEAKER_00] i meni dragom prijatelju

284
00:18:47,720 --> 00:18:49,339
[SPEAKER_00] koji je ubijen prošle godine.

285
00:18:53,339 --> 00:18:55,200
[SPEAKER_00] U poriču sam se osjećala

286
00:18:55,200 --> 00:18:57,819
[SPEAKER_00] jako izgubljeno,

287
00:18:57,819 --> 00:19:00,259
[SPEAKER_00] bila sam osuđivana

288
00:19:00,259 --> 00:19:03,299
[SPEAKER_00] i neprihvaćena od društva.

289
00:19:03,299 --> 00:19:07,319
[SPEAKER_00] Nitko mi nije dao šansu,

290
00:19:07,319 --> 00:19:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] nisam se mogla zaposliti,

291
00:19:10,000 --> 00:19:13,299
[SPEAKER_00] jednom osuđenu, uvijek osuđena.

292
00:19:14,700 --> 00:19:16,500
[SPEAKER_00] Dva, tri dana sam bila dobro,

293
00:19:16,500 --> 00:19:18,619
[SPEAKER_00] pa sam opet pala,

294
00:19:18,619 --> 00:19:20,500
[SPEAKER_00] pa sam trčala na ispovjed.

295
00:19:20,500 --> 00:19:22,519
[SPEAKER_00] Uglavnom nisam bila

296
00:19:22,519 --> 00:19:24,099
[SPEAKER_00] ni vamo, ni tamo.

297
00:19:24,099 --> 00:19:28,319
[SPEAKER_00] Treći put odlazim u Međugorje

298
00:19:28,319 --> 00:19:30,619
[SPEAKER_00] sa zajednicom Krvi Kristove.

299
00:19:33,000 --> 00:19:35,720
[SPEAKER_00] U Međugorju tada je bilo jako teško,

300
00:19:35,720 --> 00:19:38,460
[SPEAKER_00] imala sam jake reakcije,

301
00:19:38,460 --> 00:19:41,960
[SPEAKER_00] te uspinjanja na brdo Ukazanja

302
00:19:41,960 --> 00:19:43,839
[SPEAKER_00] i na brdo Križjevac

303
00:19:43,839 --> 00:19:46,180
[SPEAKER_00] bila su jako teška,

304
00:19:46,180 --> 00:19:50,019
[SPEAKER_00] ali uz Isusovu i Gospinu pomoć

305
00:19:50,019 --> 00:19:51,539
[SPEAKER_00] i mog duhovnika

306
00:19:51,539 --> 00:19:53,799
[SPEAKER_00] i par dragih ljudi

307
00:19:53,799 --> 00:19:55,460
[SPEAKER_00] iz zajednice Krvi Kristove

308
00:19:55,460 --> 00:19:58,380
[SPEAKER_00] koji su godina vam pratili na molitvama,

309
00:19:58,380 --> 00:19:59,920
[SPEAKER_00] mi smo uspjeli.

310
00:20:01,779 --> 00:20:03,220
[SPEAKER_00] Nakon Međugorja

311
00:20:03,220 --> 00:20:05,660
[SPEAKER_00] opet se vraćam u poreć,

312
00:20:05,660 --> 00:20:07,799
[SPEAKER_00] opet ista priča,

313
00:20:07,799 --> 00:20:10,160
[SPEAKER_00] borba između dobra i zla,

314
00:20:10,160 --> 00:20:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] sve ta misa, ispovjed,

315
00:20:13,000 --> 00:20:15,240
[SPEAKER_00] vrtila sam se u krug

316
00:20:15,240 --> 00:20:16,380
[SPEAKER_00] sama sa sobom.

317
00:20:16,380 --> 00:20:20,099
[SPEAKER_00] Jedan dan

318
00:20:20,099 --> 00:20:21,839
[SPEAKER_00] doumila sam se

319
00:20:21,839 --> 00:20:23,319
[SPEAKER_00] da li ću išći na svetu misu

320
00:20:23,319 --> 00:20:25,500
[SPEAKER_00] ili ću opet pokleknuti zlu.

321
00:20:25,500 --> 00:20:29,660
[SPEAKER_00] Pala sam nakon jedne kriminalne radnje,

322
00:20:30,059 --> 00:20:32,339
[SPEAKER_00] te odlazim drugi put u zatvor.

323
00:20:34,380 --> 00:20:36,440
[SPEAKER_00] s obzirom da prvi zatvor

324
00:20:36,440 --> 00:20:38,519
[SPEAKER_00] nisam doživjela,

325
00:20:38,519 --> 00:20:40,819
[SPEAKER_00] jer sam bila prisilno stavljena

326
00:20:40,819 --> 00:20:42,220
[SPEAKER_00] na svakakve tablete

327
00:20:42,220 --> 00:20:43,759
[SPEAKER_00] i inekcije,

328
00:20:43,759 --> 00:20:45,660
[SPEAKER_00] te su me jednom zato

329
00:20:45,660 --> 00:20:47,140
[SPEAKER_00] jer sam odbijala terapiju,

330
00:20:47,140 --> 00:20:48,900
[SPEAKER_00] zatvorili ju sami,

331
00:20:48,900 --> 00:20:50,160
[SPEAKER_00] su vezali za krevete.

332
00:20:53,660 --> 00:20:55,079
[SPEAKER_00] drugi put u zatvoru

333
00:20:55,079 --> 00:20:58,539
[SPEAKER_00] sam u potpunosti bila svjesna svega,

334
00:20:58,539 --> 00:21:01,039
[SPEAKER_00] osjećala sam se jadno,

335
00:21:01,039 --> 00:21:02,559
[SPEAKER_00] nemočno,

336
00:21:02,559 --> 00:21:04,480
[SPEAKER_00] pritisak je bio velik,

337
00:21:04,480 --> 00:21:07,039
[SPEAKER_00] a najviše u meni,

338
00:21:07,039 --> 00:21:09,940
[SPEAKER_00] jer sam počela biti svjesna

339
00:21:09,940 --> 00:21:11,519
[SPEAKER_00] svega što sam napravila,

340
00:21:11,519 --> 00:21:13,839
[SPEAKER_00] a najviše zla sam nanjela

341
00:21:13,839 --> 00:21:14,700
[SPEAKER_00] sama sebi.

342
00:21:14,700 --> 00:21:18,680
[SPEAKER_00] Cijeli život mi je prolazio

343
00:21:18,680 --> 00:21:19,480
[SPEAKER_00] kroz glavu,

344
00:21:19,480 --> 00:21:22,440
[SPEAKER_00] još gore mi je bilo,

345
00:21:22,440 --> 00:21:23,240
[SPEAKER_00] jer moja mama

346
00:21:23,240 --> 00:21:26,240
[SPEAKER_00] vani se spremala na operaciju,

347
00:21:28,559 --> 00:21:29,660
[SPEAKER_00] imala je rak dojke,

348
00:21:29,660 --> 00:21:33,180
[SPEAKER_00] a moja sestra je bila trudna

349
00:21:33,180 --> 00:21:34,339
[SPEAKER_00] sa drugim djetetom

350
00:21:34,339 --> 00:21:36,619
[SPEAKER_00] i bila je pred porodom.

351
00:21:36,619 --> 00:21:41,299
[SPEAKER_00] Prolazili su dani,

352
00:21:41,299 --> 00:21:44,680
[SPEAKER_00] padala sam u sve veću depresiju,

353
00:21:44,680 --> 00:21:47,319
[SPEAKER_00] dok nisam shvatila

354
00:21:47,319 --> 00:21:49,779
[SPEAKER_00] da sam nitkoj ništa bez Boga,

355
00:21:49,779 --> 00:21:53,579
[SPEAKER_00] te sam mu se odlučila vratiti

356
00:21:53,579 --> 00:21:55,799
[SPEAKER_00] našem jedinom spasitelju,

357
00:21:55,799 --> 00:21:56,859
[SPEAKER_00] gospodinu našem,

358
00:21:56,859 --> 00:21:57,859
[SPEAKER_00] Isusu Hristu.

359
00:21:58,559 --> 00:22:01,200
[SPEAKER_00] To je bilo vrijeme korone,

360
00:22:01,200 --> 00:22:05,259
[SPEAKER_00] posjete nisu bile dopuštene,

361
00:22:05,259 --> 00:22:07,559
[SPEAKER_00] ali čudom Božjim

362
00:22:07,559 --> 00:22:09,759
[SPEAKER_00] dopustili su da moj duhovnik,

363
00:22:09,759 --> 00:22:10,940
[SPEAKER_00] Pater Ilija,

364
00:22:10,940 --> 00:22:13,619
[SPEAKER_00] dođe meni u posjetu

365
00:22:13,619 --> 00:22:14,960
[SPEAKER_00] i da me ispovijedi.

366
00:22:14,960 --> 00:22:18,039
[SPEAKER_00] U zatvoru u Puli

367
00:22:18,039 --> 00:22:23,839
[SPEAKER_00] vršio se jako velik pritisak na mene

368
00:22:23,839 --> 00:22:27,079
[SPEAKER_00] i od strane zatvorenika

369
00:22:27,079 --> 00:22:29,440
[SPEAKER_00] i od strane zatvorskog sustava,

370
00:22:29,440 --> 00:22:32,660
[SPEAKER_00] jer sam bila jedina žena

371
00:22:32,660 --> 00:22:34,859
[SPEAKER_00] na izdržavanju kazne zatvora

372
00:22:34,859 --> 00:22:36,079
[SPEAKER_00] u muškom zatvoru,

373
00:22:36,079 --> 00:22:38,720
[SPEAKER_00] jer sam nekad bila

374
00:22:38,720 --> 00:22:40,319
[SPEAKER_00] medijske eksponirana osoba.

375
00:22:42,720 --> 00:22:47,140
[SPEAKER_00] i u zatvoru u Puli sam završila nepravednu samici,

376
00:22:47,140 --> 00:22:50,839
[SPEAKER_00] dok sam bila u sobi sa više žena,

377
00:22:50,839 --> 00:22:53,720
[SPEAKER_00] te su se zatvorenice odružile

378
00:22:53,720 --> 00:22:57,079
[SPEAKER_00] i pisale izjavu protiv mene

379
00:22:57,079 --> 00:22:59,099
[SPEAKER_00] da bi završila u samici,

380
00:22:59,099 --> 00:23:00,720
[SPEAKER_00] što se i na kraju desilo.

381
00:23:01,500 --> 00:23:06,079
[SPEAKER_00] Na kraju jedna zatvorenica se slomila na ispitivanju,

382
00:23:06,079 --> 00:23:09,480
[SPEAKER_00] jer im se priče nisu poklapale

383
00:23:09,480 --> 00:23:13,519
[SPEAKER_00] i priznala istinu da su se dogovorile i lagale,

384
00:23:13,519 --> 00:23:16,700
[SPEAKER_00] te su me odlučili vratiti na odjel

385
00:23:16,700 --> 00:23:18,079
[SPEAKER_00] i izdvojiti od svih

386
00:23:18,079 --> 00:23:20,619
[SPEAKER_00] i smestiti u sobu samu.

387
00:23:23,220 --> 00:23:26,400
[SPEAKER_00] Osam mjeseci sam provela u zatvoru u Puli.

388
00:23:26,400 --> 00:23:35,559
[SPEAKER_00] Do kraja kazne mi je ostalo šest mjeseci.

389
00:23:35,559 --> 00:23:40,839
[SPEAKER_00] U zakonu piše da kaznu do šest mjeseci

390
00:23:40,839 --> 00:23:45,519
[SPEAKER_00] zatvorenik služi u zatvoru po mjestu prebivališta.

391
00:23:45,519 --> 00:23:47,619
[SPEAKER_00] Za mene je to bila Pula.

392
00:23:47,619 --> 00:23:52,220
[SPEAKER_00] Unatoč tome stigao je papir

393
00:23:52,220 --> 00:23:56,980
[SPEAKER_00] da budem premještena u ženski zatvor u Požegi,

394
00:23:56,980 --> 00:24:00,279
[SPEAKER_00] u još gori zatvor, bez razloga.

395
00:24:00,279 --> 00:24:06,680
[SPEAKER_00] Nedavno sam saznala prave razloge.

396
00:24:06,680 --> 00:24:11,259
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto sam premještena?

397
00:24:11,259 --> 00:24:14,720
[SPEAKER_00] Nisam tražila istinu,

398
00:24:14,720 --> 00:24:17,619
[SPEAKER_00] ali Isus je rekao

399
00:24:17,619 --> 00:24:20,980
[SPEAKER_00] ako ostanete u mojoj riječi,

400
00:24:21,220 --> 00:24:23,279
[SPEAKER_00] u istinu mojste učenici,

401
00:24:23,279 --> 00:24:24,980
[SPEAKER_00] upoznat ćete istinu,

402
00:24:24,980 --> 00:24:27,220
[SPEAKER_00] istina će vas osloboditi.

403
00:24:28,980 --> 00:24:33,680
[SPEAKER_00] nekad prije bi išla ganjati pravdu ili se osvetiti,

404
00:24:35,740 --> 00:24:37,980
[SPEAKER_00] ali danas moja osveta je oprost,

405
00:24:37,980 --> 00:24:40,839
[SPEAKER_00] kao što je rekao naš blaženi Miroslav Bulešić.

406
00:24:46,740 --> 00:24:53,900
[SPEAKER_00] od zatvoru u Požegi sam još manje znala ono što vam mogu reći,

407
00:24:53,900 --> 00:24:56,420
[SPEAKER_00] da to mjesto ne bi poželjela nikome.

408
00:24:58,359 --> 00:25:01,160
[SPEAKER_00] za vrijeme mog boravka u zatvoru u Požegi,

409
00:25:01,160 --> 00:25:05,619
[SPEAKER_00] bila sam svjedoka da tamo ima još više droge,

410
00:25:05,619 --> 00:25:09,819
[SPEAKER_00] silovanja, maltretiranja,

411
00:25:09,819 --> 00:25:11,359
[SPEAKER_00] naselja,

412
00:25:11,359 --> 00:25:12,599
[SPEAKER_00] nemorala,

413
00:25:14,519 --> 00:25:16,019
[SPEAKER_00] luda između istog spola.

414
00:25:16,019 --> 00:25:25,519
[SPEAKER_00] U Požegi sam skoro i sama postala žrtva silovanja,

415
00:25:25,519 --> 00:25:27,299
[SPEAKER_00] ali Bogu hvala nisam.

416
00:25:34,440 --> 00:25:37,319
[SPEAKER_00] Nakon godinu i pol provedenih u zatvoru,

417
00:25:37,319 --> 00:25:40,079
[SPEAKER_00] 11.11.

418
00:25:40,079 --> 00:25:42,599
[SPEAKER_00] izlazim iz zatvora

419
00:25:42,599 --> 00:25:44,740
[SPEAKER_00] na vlak dan Svetog Martina,

420
00:25:44,740 --> 00:25:48,799
[SPEAKER_00] zaštitnika Svetog Lovreća,

421
00:25:48,799 --> 00:25:52,079
[SPEAKER_00] gdje sam isto na poziv svećenika

422
00:25:52,079 --> 00:25:55,400
[SPEAKER_00] posvjedočila Božju ljubav u mom životu.

423
00:25:55,400 --> 00:25:57,660
[SPEAKER_00] U sveto dan,

424
00:25:57,660 --> 00:26:00,319
[SPEAKER_00] kad sam drugi put izašla iz zatvora,

425
00:26:00,319 --> 00:26:02,579
[SPEAKER_00] je isto bio četvrtak,

426
00:26:02,579 --> 00:26:04,420
[SPEAKER_00] ali opet ne je bilo koji četvrtak,

427
00:26:04,440 --> 00:26:06,240
[SPEAKER_00] nego 15. četvrtak

428
00:26:06,240 --> 00:26:07,700
[SPEAKER_00] po molitvi Svetoj Riti.

429
00:26:07,700 --> 00:26:11,720
[SPEAKER_00] Nakon izlazka iz zatvora,

430
00:26:11,720 --> 00:26:13,119
[SPEAKER_00] odlazim

431
00:26:13,119 --> 00:26:17,420
[SPEAKER_00] u centar pomirenja u prozorju,

432
00:26:17,420 --> 00:26:19,559
[SPEAKER_00] to je Samostani crkva

433
00:26:19,559 --> 00:26:21,500
[SPEAKER_00] misjonara Krvi Kristove,

434
00:26:21,500 --> 00:26:24,940
[SPEAKER_00] gdje sam ostala mjesec dana

435
00:26:24,940 --> 00:26:28,319
[SPEAKER_00] u molitvi i adaptaciji na slobodu.

436
00:26:28,319 --> 00:26:32,859
[SPEAKER_00] Jedan dan moja sestra mi je došla

437
00:26:32,859 --> 00:26:35,460
[SPEAKER_00] i rekla da je dobila u molitvi

438
00:26:35,460 --> 00:26:37,259
[SPEAKER_00] poticaj Duha Svetoga,

439
00:26:37,259 --> 00:26:39,960
[SPEAKER_00] da bi trebala otići u Međugorje.

440
00:26:39,960 --> 00:26:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tada ja to još nisam osjetila,

441
00:26:43,000 --> 00:26:46,400
[SPEAKER_00] ali u Zagrebu se nisam osjećala dobro.

442
00:26:49,119 --> 00:26:50,599
[SPEAKER_00] vratila sam se u Poreć,

443
00:26:50,599 --> 00:26:54,200
[SPEAKER_00] na svetoj misiji u Poreću,

444
00:26:54,200 --> 00:26:56,960
[SPEAKER_00] bilo je vanđelje po Mateju,

445
00:26:56,960 --> 00:27:01,480
[SPEAKER_00] jer tko hoće spasiti svoj život,

446
00:27:01,480 --> 00:27:02,640
[SPEAKER_00] izgubit će ga,

447
00:27:02,640 --> 00:27:05,220
[SPEAKER_00] a tko zbog mene izgubi svoj život,

448
00:27:05,220 --> 00:27:06,220
[SPEAKER_00] naći će ga.

449
00:27:07,380 --> 00:27:09,319
[SPEAKER_00] I upravo tada sam osjetila u srcu,

450
00:27:09,319 --> 00:27:10,680
[SPEAKER_00] te sam otišla u Međugorje.

451
00:27:10,680 --> 00:27:15,900
[SPEAKER_00] 2022. novu godinu

452
00:27:15,900 --> 00:27:19,339
[SPEAKER_00] dočekala sam u Međugorju.

453
00:27:21,420 --> 00:27:23,579
[SPEAKER_00] Samo bi se htjela kratko vratiti

454
00:27:23,579 --> 00:27:24,720
[SPEAKER_00] na onaj period,

455
00:27:24,720 --> 00:27:26,940
[SPEAKER_00] nakon izlaska iz zatvora,

456
00:27:26,940 --> 00:27:30,039
[SPEAKER_00] kada sam bila u centru pomirenja u Prozorju.

457
00:27:30,039 --> 00:27:32,880
[SPEAKER_00] Moja sestra poslala mi je

458
00:27:32,880 --> 00:27:35,359
[SPEAKER_00] svjedočanstvo od mog dragog brata,

459
00:27:35,359 --> 00:27:36,900
[SPEAKER_00] Gorana Čurkovića.

460
00:27:36,900 --> 00:27:39,799
[SPEAKER_00] Pogledala sam njegovo svjedočanstvo

461
00:27:39,799 --> 00:27:42,079
[SPEAKER_00] i svidjelo mi se jako,

462
00:27:42,079 --> 00:27:46,180
[SPEAKER_00] jer su nam životne priče slične.

463
00:27:46,180 --> 00:27:49,339
[SPEAKER_00] Od tada Goran i Katarina

464
00:27:49,339 --> 00:27:51,160
[SPEAKER_00] su meni ostali u srcu,

465
00:27:51,420 --> 00:27:53,539
[SPEAKER_00] te sam ih svakodnevno prikazivala

466
00:27:53,539 --> 00:27:54,579
[SPEAKER_00] na svetim misama.

467
00:27:54,579 --> 00:27:58,380
[SPEAKER_00] I kada sam došla u Međugorje,

468
00:27:58,380 --> 00:28:01,660
[SPEAKER_00] otišla sam na večernju svetu misu

469
00:28:01,660 --> 00:28:04,500
[SPEAKER_00] na koju sam prikazala Gorana

470
00:28:04,500 --> 00:28:05,740
[SPEAKER_00] i njegovu obitelj.

471
00:28:05,740 --> 00:28:08,299
[SPEAKER_00] Izlazim iz crkve

472
00:28:08,299 --> 00:28:10,480
[SPEAKER_00] i kad ni manje ni više

473
00:28:10,480 --> 00:28:12,539
[SPEAKER_00] u crkve bio naslonjen baš Goran.

474
00:28:12,539 --> 00:28:15,539
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da gospa mi odmah uslišila molitvu.

475
00:28:15,539 --> 00:28:19,299
[SPEAKER_00] Počeli smo se družiti.

476
00:28:19,299 --> 00:28:21,299
[SPEAKER_00] Goran i Katarina su mi

477
00:28:21,299 --> 00:28:22,539
[SPEAKER_00] jako puno pomogli.

478
00:28:22,539 --> 00:28:25,039
[SPEAKER_00] I tada i dan danas smo prijatelji

479
00:28:25,039 --> 00:28:27,220
[SPEAKER_00] i jako sam im zahvalna na svemu.

480
00:28:27,220 --> 00:28:30,559
[SPEAKER_00] Otišla sam u Međugorje

481
00:28:30,559 --> 00:28:33,380
[SPEAKER_00] sa nakanom da ostanem deve dana

482
00:28:33,380 --> 00:28:36,279
[SPEAKER_00] i izmolim devetnicu svetoj Riti

483
00:28:36,279 --> 00:28:40,559
[SPEAKER_00] misleći da će u deve dana

484
00:28:40,559 --> 00:28:42,500
[SPEAKER_00] meni Isus sve riješiti.

485
00:28:43,339 --> 00:28:45,400
[SPEAKER_00] ostala sam na kraju više od dvije godine.

486
00:28:47,079 --> 00:28:50,819
[SPEAKER_00] tokom prve devetnice sveto Riti

487
00:28:50,819 --> 00:28:56,700
[SPEAKER_00] shvatila sam da mi je potrebna još jedna

488
00:28:56,700 --> 00:28:59,920
[SPEAKER_00] te sam odlučila produžiti moj boravak

489
00:28:59,920 --> 00:29:02,660
[SPEAKER_00] i tako sam izmolila ne jednu

490
00:29:02,660 --> 00:29:04,539
[SPEAKER_00] nego puno više devetnica.

491
00:29:05,900 --> 00:29:08,099
[SPEAKER_00] zatim sam se preselila u stan

492
00:29:08,099 --> 00:29:10,579
[SPEAKER_00] i shvatila da će moj boravak

493
00:29:10,579 --> 00:29:12,440
[SPEAKER_00] u Međugorju biti duži

494
00:29:12,440 --> 00:29:13,880
[SPEAKER_00] nego što sam mislila.

495
00:29:13,880 --> 00:29:17,859
[SPEAKER_00] Što se tiče financijskih mogućnosti

496
00:29:17,859 --> 00:29:19,079
[SPEAKER_00] nisam ih imala

497
00:29:19,140 --> 00:29:21,740
[SPEAKER_00] tek sam izašla iz zatvora.

498
00:29:21,740 --> 00:29:24,460
[SPEAKER_00] Imala sam Isusa i Mariju

499
00:29:24,460 --> 00:29:27,099
[SPEAKER_00] i moju obitelj koji su mi pomagali.

500
00:29:27,099 --> 00:29:31,599
[SPEAKER_00] U Međugorju sam bila baš kada

501
00:29:31,599 --> 00:29:33,400
[SPEAKER_00] nije bilo sezone

502
00:29:33,400 --> 00:29:36,680
[SPEAKER_00] te mogućnost zaposlenja je bila nikakva

503
00:29:36,680 --> 00:29:39,920
[SPEAKER_00] ali Bog je providio točnost

504
00:29:39,920 --> 00:29:42,480
[SPEAKER_00] u svakom periodu mog života

505
00:29:42,480 --> 00:29:45,119
[SPEAKER_00] koga mi treba i zašto poslati.

506
00:29:46,359 --> 00:29:48,960
[SPEAKER_00] Sada mislim da sam baš točno

507
00:29:48,960 --> 00:29:50,240
[SPEAKER_00] u tom razdoblju života

508
00:29:50,240 --> 00:29:52,299
[SPEAKER_00] trebala biti u Međugorju

509
00:29:52,299 --> 00:29:55,160
[SPEAKER_00] i posvetiti se osobnoj molitvi

510
00:29:55,160 --> 00:29:57,700
[SPEAKER_00] to jest mom odnosu sa Bogom.

511
00:29:57,700 --> 00:30:01,720
[SPEAKER_00] Falili su mi segmenti

512
00:30:01,720 --> 00:30:03,339
[SPEAKER_00] i u ponašanju

513
00:30:03,339 --> 00:30:04,660
[SPEAKER_00] a i u odjevanju

514
00:30:04,660 --> 00:30:05,759
[SPEAKER_00] i dostojanstvu

515
00:30:05,759 --> 00:30:08,559
[SPEAKER_00] do kojeg ja kao žena nisam imala

516
00:30:08,559 --> 00:30:11,319
[SPEAKER_00] i nisam shvaćala koliko je to bitno

517
00:30:11,319 --> 00:30:15,519
[SPEAKER_00] da nisam odgovorna samo za svoje grijehe

518
00:30:15,519 --> 00:30:17,880
[SPEAKER_00] nego i za grijehe drugih osoba

519
00:30:17,880 --> 00:30:21,579
[SPEAKER_00] ako sam ja tako ja potičem svojim odjevanjem

520
00:30:21,579 --> 00:30:24,559
[SPEAKER_00] i ponašanjem druge muškarce na grijeh.

521
00:30:24,559 --> 00:30:28,880
[SPEAKER_00] Svaki dan sam išla na brdu ukazanja

522
00:30:28,880 --> 00:30:30,400
[SPEAKER_00] i na križevac

523
00:30:30,400 --> 00:30:34,119
[SPEAKER_00] moj grijesi su mi bili stalno pred očima

524
00:30:34,119 --> 00:30:38,559
[SPEAKER_00] u početku uspinjanja su mi bila jako teška

525
00:30:38,559 --> 00:30:41,099
[SPEAKER_00] ali nakon svakog uspinjanja

526
00:30:41,099 --> 00:30:43,059
[SPEAKER_00] vraćala sam se dole lakša.

527
00:30:45,200 --> 00:30:47,559
[SPEAKER_00] Počela sam se penjati samo noću

528
00:30:47,559 --> 00:30:50,400
[SPEAKER_00] jer sam shvatila da je to još teže

529
00:30:50,400 --> 00:30:53,559
[SPEAKER_00] ali s obzirom na život koji sam živjela

530
00:30:53,559 --> 00:30:56,640
[SPEAKER_00] to je bilo najmanje što sam mogla učiniti

531
00:30:56,640 --> 00:30:59,200
[SPEAKER_00] kao zadovoljštinu za svoje grijehe.

532
00:30:59,559 --> 00:31:02,299
[SPEAKER_00] Ići svaki dan na brdu ukazanja

533
00:31:02,299 --> 00:31:04,180
[SPEAKER_00] na brdu križevac

534
00:31:04,180 --> 00:31:06,140
[SPEAKER_00] na molitveni program.

535
00:31:06,140 --> 00:31:10,079
[SPEAKER_00] Penjala sam se isključivo noću

536
00:31:10,079 --> 00:31:14,079
[SPEAKER_00] neovisno o vremenskim uvjetima.

537
00:31:14,079 --> 00:31:18,559
[SPEAKER_00] Poslije mojh anžela Gorana i Katarine

538
00:31:18,559 --> 00:31:20,680
[SPEAKER_00] Isus mi je poslao

539
00:31:20,680 --> 00:31:24,839
[SPEAKER_00] na životni put fra Borisa Baruna

540
00:31:24,839 --> 00:31:29,119
[SPEAKER_00] i 11.2. na gospu Lursku

541
00:31:29,119 --> 00:31:31,460
[SPEAKER_00] Bog me poslao još jednog anžela

542
00:31:31,460 --> 00:31:35,180
[SPEAKER_00] a to je nadbiskup Aldo Cavalli

543
00:31:35,180 --> 00:31:38,220
[SPEAKER_00] on je apostolski vizitator u Međugorju

544
00:31:38,220 --> 00:31:40,819
[SPEAKER_00] koji mi je jako puno pomogao

545
00:31:40,819 --> 00:31:43,500
[SPEAKER_00] skupa sa fra Borisom Barunom iz Međugorja.

546
00:31:43,500 --> 00:31:47,700
[SPEAKER_00] Prvu zimu sam bila posvećena

547
00:31:47,700 --> 00:31:51,539
[SPEAKER_00] osobnoj molitvi i odnosu sa Bogom

548
00:31:51,539 --> 00:31:53,799
[SPEAKER_00] te su i tada molili intenzivno molitve

549
00:31:53,799 --> 00:31:55,240
[SPEAKER_00] egzorcizma nadamnom.

550
00:31:55,240 --> 00:31:58,680
[SPEAKER_00] Do ljeta puno sam se bolje osjećala

551
00:31:58,680 --> 00:32:01,019
[SPEAKER_00] te sam počela tražiti posao

552
00:32:01,019 --> 00:32:04,019
[SPEAKER_00] dobila sam posao u jednoj suvenirnici

553
00:32:04,019 --> 00:32:07,380
[SPEAKER_00] poslije u jednom hotelu na recepciji

554
00:32:07,380 --> 00:32:09,359
[SPEAKER_00] i na kraju u jednoj vinariji.

555
00:32:09,359 --> 00:32:11,619
[SPEAKER_00] Nije bilo lako

556
00:32:11,619 --> 00:32:14,019
[SPEAKER_00] okolnosti nisu bile svaki dašnje

557
00:32:14,019 --> 00:32:18,740
[SPEAKER_00] tako da sam promijenila i poslova i stanova u Međugorju.

558
00:32:21,740 --> 00:32:26,079
[SPEAKER_00] teško je da faza pročišćenja bude prejednostavna,

559
00:32:26,079 --> 00:32:33,779
[SPEAKER_00] prejednostavna, no ja vam želim posvjedočiti da sam dobila jako puno milosti od Isusa i Gospe.

560
00:32:34,779 --> 00:32:40,059
[SPEAKER_00] prošla je godina dana da sam se vratila iz Međugorja u Hrvatsku.

561
00:32:40,059 --> 00:32:46,400
[SPEAKER_00] koji je Božji plan za mene ne znam u potpunosti,

562
00:32:46,400 --> 00:32:49,119
[SPEAKER_00] ali znam da mu beskljeno vjerujem.

563
00:32:49,119 --> 00:32:52,640
[SPEAKER_00] Znam da mi je dao novi identitet,

564
00:32:52,640 --> 00:32:55,940
[SPEAKER_00] da sam napokon mogla spoznati da sam

565
00:32:55,940 --> 00:32:59,359
[SPEAKER_00] njegova ljubljena kćer, njegova princeza.

566
00:32:59,359 --> 00:33:03,960
[SPEAKER_00] Znam da je jedino On imao moć

567
00:33:03,960 --> 00:33:06,900
[SPEAKER_00] obnoviti moje dostojanstvo kao žene,

568
00:33:06,900 --> 00:33:11,960
[SPEAKER_00] ispuniti moj život istinskom radošću i dati mir.

569
00:33:11,960 --> 00:33:16,200
[SPEAKER_00] To je mir i ispunjenje koje sam dugo tražila,

570
00:33:16,400 --> 00:33:18,099
[SPEAKER_00] na krivim mjestima.

571
00:33:18,099 --> 00:33:20,799
[SPEAKER_00] Znam još jednu stvar,

572
00:33:20,799 --> 00:33:24,319
[SPEAKER_00] da želim biti dobra katolkinja

573
00:33:24,319 --> 00:33:26,619
[SPEAKER_00] i dobra osoba,

574
00:33:26,619 --> 00:33:30,740
[SPEAKER_00] te mu na taj način odgovoriti na darovanu ljubav.

575
00:33:30,740 --> 00:33:35,660
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim da je to moja najveća zadaća na ovom zemljskom životu.

576
00:33:35,660 --> 00:33:40,680
[SPEAKER_00] Danas svakodnevno odlazim na svetu misu

577
00:33:40,680 --> 00:33:42,900
[SPEAKER_00] i dalje molim gospodina

578
00:33:42,900 --> 00:33:45,559
[SPEAKER_00] danas...

579
00:33:46,400 --> 00:34:04,220
[SPEAKER_00] Svakodnevno odlazim na svetu misu.

580
00:34:06,220 --> 00:34:09,079
[SPEAKER_00] molim tri krunice dnevno.

581
00:34:09,079 --> 00:34:14,800
[SPEAKER_00] Tri godine trudim se i živim sakramentalni život

582
00:34:14,800 --> 00:34:19,500
[SPEAKER_00] i obavezno molim krunicu božanskog milosrđa u 15 sati.

583
00:34:21,239 --> 00:34:22,760
[SPEAKER_00] Vama divnim ljudima,

584
00:34:22,760 --> 00:34:25,219
[SPEAKER_00] za kraj,

585
00:34:25,219 --> 00:34:27,679
[SPEAKER_00] želim poslat poruku.

586
00:34:27,679 --> 00:34:32,360
[SPEAKER_00] Moj život svjedoči

587
00:34:32,360 --> 00:34:36,820
[SPEAKER_00] da ne morate prolaziti kroz tolike muke i boli

588
00:34:36,820 --> 00:34:41,699
[SPEAKER_00] koje su posljedica pristajanja na džavlove ponude,

589
00:34:42,820 --> 00:34:44,760
[SPEAKER_00] koje nudi u svijetu kroz novac,

590
00:34:44,760 --> 00:34:46,159
[SPEAKER_00] luksuz,

591
00:34:46,159 --> 00:34:48,119
[SPEAKER_00] prestiž, moć,

592
00:34:48,119 --> 00:34:49,659
[SPEAKER_00] kriminal i drogu.

593
00:34:49,659 --> 00:34:55,900
[SPEAKER_00] Radije je potrčite direktno njemu u zagrljaj,

594
00:34:55,900 --> 00:35:03,380
[SPEAKER_00] jer je on sam zaista izvor žive vode od koje nećete ožedniti nikada.

595
00:35:05,400 --> 00:35:07,360
[SPEAKER_00] Ukoliko ste i sami u ropstvima

596
00:35:07,360 --> 00:35:11,480
[SPEAKER_00] i tada, znajte, nema nikoga moćnijeg i milosrdnijeg

597
00:35:11,480 --> 00:35:13,539
[SPEAKER_00] od našeg gospodina Isusa Krista,

598
00:35:13,539 --> 00:35:14,880
[SPEAKER_00] koji vas trpljivo čeka.

599
00:35:14,880 --> 00:35:20,300
[SPEAKER_00] Zahvaljujem se gospodinu našem Isusu Kristu

600
00:35:20,300 --> 00:35:24,360
[SPEAKER_00] i našoj ljubljenoj majci Mariji na svim milostima

601
00:35:24,360 --> 00:35:27,639
[SPEAKER_00] te osobito na današnjoj milosti

602
00:35:27,639 --> 00:35:30,440
[SPEAKER_00] što sam mogla posvjedočiti neizmjernu Božju ljubav

603
00:35:30,440 --> 00:35:35,179
[SPEAKER_00] i milosrđe koje je samo našem dragom Bogu moguće

604
00:35:35,179 --> 00:35:38,760
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala moje dragoj braći Miši

605
00:35:38,760 --> 00:35:41,179
[SPEAKER_00] i mati koje u lajvu

606
00:35:41,179 --> 00:35:45,460
[SPEAKER_00] što su me pozvali da posvjedočim Božju ljubav.

607
00:35:45,460 --> 00:35:48,139
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala svima vama.

608
00:35:48,139 --> 00:35:51,860
[SPEAKER_00] Nadam se da nisam bila preduga ili predosadna.

609
00:35:51,860 --> 00:35:53,860
[SPEAKER_00] Slava i hvala Isusu. Amen.

